Project description

tensorflow/datasets is a library of public datasets ready to use withTensorFlow. Each dataset definition contains the logic necessary to download andprepare the dataset, as well as to read it into a model using thetf.data.Dataset API.

Usage outside of TensorFlow is also supported.

See the README on GitHub for further documentation.
